 id=\"note9e\" data-full-marker=\"9e\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830632\" id=\"note9e_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.29-30?lang=fra#p29\">Hél 3:29–30</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.22?lang=fra#p22\">D&amp;A 132:22</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note10a\" data-full-marker=\"10a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830633\" id=\"note10a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/belief-believe?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Croire</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note10b\" data-full-marker=\"10b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830634\" id=\"note10b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/book-of-mormon?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Livre de Mormon</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note10c\" data-full-marker=\"10c\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830635\" id=\"note10c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.27-29?lang=fra#p27\">Mro 10:27–29</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note10d\" data-full-marker=\"10d\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830636\" id=\"note10d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.28?lang=fra#p28\">2 Né 25:28</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"11\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note11a\" data-full-marker=\"11a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830637\" id=\"note11a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/ether/5.4?lang=fra#p4\">Ét 5:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.35?lang=fra#p35\">Mro 7:35</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note11b\" data-full-marker=\"11b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117830638\" id=\"note11b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/rev/20.12?lang=fra#p12\">Ap 20:12</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.34?lang=fra#p34\">Mro 10:34</a>.</p>\